Palindrome String

Given a string S, check if it is palindrome or not.

Example 1:

Input: S = "abba"
Output: 1
Explanation: S is a palindrome
Example 2:

Input: S = "abc" 
Output: 0
Explanation: S is not a palindrome

CODING:
class Solution {
    int isPalindrome(String S) {
        // code here
        int n=S.length();
        for(int i=0;i<n/2;i++)
        {
            if(S.charAt(i)!=S.charAt(n-1-i))
            {
                return 0;
            }
        }
            return 1;
        
    }
};
